The Elder's important business
#show Hero 1
#show Elder 2
#ANIMATION 9
#CAMERA 9
#phrase Elder  1
Oh Chosen! I put together all the rumors, legends and lore of our village elders and came to an amazing conclusion - our island is not so isolated as it seems. We must find out if this is indeed true, and if you could find a way to communicate with other lands - with my humble assistance, of course - our village would be tremendously happy...
#ANIMATION 30
#NOLIPS
#CAMERA 2 0 2.2 2
#phrase Hero  2
Oh!... Well, I am sure that in other lands I could find really powerful Magicians who would restore my memory! It would be much easier just to go through a Portal over there than to run all over this devastated land of Gipath!
#DESC To himself
