So tell me!
#ANIMATION 9
#CAMERA 3
#phrase Elder  4
There is a Chief of a small Goblin tribe named GoGo. He has a blue stone where one of his eyes should be. I heard that in ancient times that they used to make Portals out of such material, and those Portals could transport people from one place to another in a split second. If we could find out where that stone came from, then I could tell whether or not we have such a Portal in Gipath or not.
#ANIMATION 5
#CAMERA 2
#phrase Hero  5
An excellent idea! But where do I find that... what's his name... GoGo?
#ANIMATION 44
#CAMERA 11
#phrase Elder  6
He will come to us himself and tell us everything he knows. GoGo's tribe worships the First Goblin; they still have his skull. If we lay our hands on that sacred object, GoGo would do anything to get it back! This is what it looks like...
